after that i just kind of went home and i had a life went to 
the grocery and the dry cleaner and the movies she said 
opening next week is the fabulous baker boys in which she 
costars with jeff and beau bridges 
i had read the script about five years prior and i fell in 
love with it because its about people and there are no car 
chases and not a whole lot of pratfalls she said 
