shamir paid tribute to those who fell 
to prevent a repeat of the suprise attack and halt any guerrilla 
infiltrations the military placed forces on high alert sunday 
israel radio said 
palestinians in the occupied west bank and gaza strip began a 
threeday strike to coincide with yom kippur and step up the 
uprising against israeli rule of the territories monday marks the 
beginning of the 23rd month of the rebellion 
the army announced saturday that travel between the occupied 
lands and israel would be barred during the holiday 
