school and schoolbased management where principals teachers 
parents and students set their own curricula agendas and plans 
he said the study he wants must provide a complete review of 
government programs that affect indian education the focus will be 
on the cost effectiveness of current efforts as well as developing 
cooperation between the bureau of indian affairs and the education 
department 
