bolars product is the only generic drug approved as 
therapeutically equivalent to macrodantin although other dosage 
forms of nitrofurantoin are available 
the fda also is investigating other generic drugs made by bolar 
as part of its probe of more than a dozen generic drug companies in 
the wake of allegations of fraud and corruption within the industry 
and fdas generic drug division 
